      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your<strong> pizza base[s]</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>tomato sauce </strong>between the<strong> pizza base[s]</strong> and spread it evenly all over with the back of a spoon</p>",
