      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard </strong>(not a mustard fan? Go easy!) in a bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
